Morning sightseeing in Munnar which includes; 
Rajamala – Eravikulam National Park, Mattupetty, Eco-Point, Tea Museum, Rose Garden etc. 
You can also enjoy Optional  boating in the Lake, Kathakali -Traditional Art form of Kerala, Kalari Payattu, Ayurvedic Massage etc. Overnight at Resort – Deluxe Room
